top_projects.name: Netflix-React-Clone
top_projects.description: Netflix Clone App 🎬🍿 This project is a Netflix clone built using React with a config-driven UI. The app dynamically fetches data from the TMDB API, rendering new content every time the page is refreshed. Users can browse trending movies and TV shows, and play trailers when they click on the posters.

top_projects.name: Olx-React-Clone
top_projects.description: OLX Clone - React & Firebase This is an OLX-like marketplace web application built with React for the frontend and Firebase for the backend. Users can sign up, log in, post products for sale, and browse product listings in real-time. Firebase is used for authentication, database storage, and image handling.

top_projects.name: TO-DO-List-App
top_projects.description: React To-Do App 🚀 This is a fully functional To-Do App built with React, showcasing key features like adding, deleting, updating, and crossing off tasks. It highlights my journey in learning React and mastering CRUD operations in a practical project.
